like an animal.

39:16.221 --> 39:18.590
I know.
I know, my bad, okay?

39:18.624 --> 39:22.160
But do you know how hard it is
to dig a six-foot grave

39:22.193 --> 39:23.662
in the rain?

39:23.695 --> 39:25.797
I just don't have that kind
of upper-body strength.

39:25.831 --> 39:29.234
The guy was an unrepentant
megalomaniac.

39:29.267 --> 39:31.937
And it made me realize
that if Dante died,

39:31.970 --> 39:35.006
Chance would need a new victim
with the golden blood

39:35.040 --> 39:36.442
to keep making product.

39:36.475 --> 39:38.009
So we searched his house.

39:38.043 --> 39:39.645
Laura: FBI!

39:39.678 --> 39:42.180
[ Groans ]

39:42.213 --> 39:43.815
Help me.

39:43.849 --> 39:45.350
Okay.
You're gonna be okay.

39:45.383 --> 39:46.852
[ Agents shouting
indistinctly in distance ]

39:46.885 --> 39:48.386
I need a medic in here,
now.

39:48.420 --> 39:50.155
Mr. Laughlin
contacted Kumiko

39:50.188 --> 39:52.858
through an Rhnull
support group website.

39:52.891 --> 39:54.793
Helping folks
with "golden blood"

39:54.826 --> 39:56.595
