the medical system.

39:56.628 --> 39:58.897
Chance lured her to Los Angeles
last week with the promise

39:58.930 --> 40:01.500
of a high-paying job,
then kidnapped her.

40:01.533 --> 40:02.901
Yeah. She was lucky.

40:02.934 --> 40:07.238
Though the trauma of her
abduction and torture

40:07.272 --> 40:09.007
