40:12.043 --> 40:14.012
I am.

40:14.045 --> 40:15.747
We solved a homicide.

40:15.781 --> 40:18.149
We saved a life.

40:18.183 --> 40:20.351
And ended
a global cosmetic conspiracy.

40:20.385 --> 40:22.588
